      "description": "**Software Engineer | Distributed Systems | TDD | AI-driven Development**\n\nWith 17+ years of experience across industries such as energy, DEX, aerospace, metallurgy, banking, marketing, and HR, I specialise in building maintainable and scalable systems.\n\n---\n\n### Core Expertise\n- Distributed systems with high availability\n- Test-Driven Development (TDD) and clean code\n- Asynchronous vs synchronous communication patterns\n- Strong focus on testing strategies and system reliability\n\n---\n\n### Approach\nI focus on delivering products that align with real user needs, combining solid engineering practices with product thinking, stakeholder empathy, and continuous improvement.\n\n---\n\n### AI in my daily work\nRecently, I have integrated Artificial Intelligence into my workflow:\n- Enhancing product capabilities\n- Improving the Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)\n- Increasing team efficiency and decision-making quality\n\n---\n\n### Side Projects\nI explore the intersection of technology and music, including a project applying Data Science to recommend chord progressions and support the songwriting process.",
